text: Innosense was an American girl group that were active from 1997 to 2003. The band was managed by Lou Pearlman and Janet Lynn Harless, who is the mother of Justin Timberlake. The members were Danay Ferrer, Mandy Ashford, Nikki DeLoach, Veronica Finn, and Amanda Latona. ==References== Category:American musical groups Category:American girl groups
